#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:950
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"看来希尔凡的情况很糟糕。莉娅虽然比以前更强大，但她不可能单枪匹马杀死他。希尔凡一定已经被方碑族和王牌精英的舰队消耗殆尽才能到达这里。你不确定你是否能救他。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:952
msgid ""
"data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append$//event[@name=\"FR_SYLVAN_INJURED\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我们无能为力。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_multiverse.xml.append:954
